(206, 1, '2015-10-27 08:34:57', '2015-10-27 08:34:57', '[:en]Srijanalaya is a nonprofit, nongovernmental organization established to create safe spaces of learning through the arts. We imagine a Nepal where <em>every </em>child has the tools necessary and the support to express and be heard.\r\n\r\n<strong>Srijanalaya</strong> comes from the words <em>srijana </em>[v] to create/imagine and <em>alaya </em>[n] a home or space.[:]', '[:en]About[:]', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2016-01-20 16:16:58', '2016-01-20 10:31:58', '', 0, 'http://srijanalaya.org/?page_id=206', 13, 'page', '', 0),
