(463, 2, '2016-01-18 23:00:55', '2016-01-18 17:15:55', '[:en]<p style="text-align: left;">The <strong>founding members</strong> are a combination of art educators, visual artists, performing artists, development professionals, and a deep knowledge of microcredits and cooperatives—a combination of idealistic values and a practical ground!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Sharareh Bajracharya</strong>     Art Educator, <em>Chairperson</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Sanjeev Maharjan           </strong>Co-founder of Drawing Room KTM, Visual Artist, <em>Vice Chairperson</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Yagya Ghale</strong>                        CEO of Nari Shakti Savings and Credit Cooperative, Talsikhel, Lalitpur, <em>Secretary</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Deepak Bajracharya</strong>        Retired UNICEF Official, <em>Treasurer</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Subima Shrestha              </strong>Founder of Nritya Aagan, Kathak Performing Artist and Teacher, <em>Member</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Sunita Maharjan</strong>               Co-founder of Drawing Room KTM, Art Educator and Visual Artist, <em>Member</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Amanda Manandhar Gurung</strong>   Executive Director of Chandra Gurung Conservation Foundation, <em>Member</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Our <strong>membership</strong> has grown to include dedicated well-wishers and collaborators.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Bhushan Shilpakar</strong>                  Co-Founder and Co-Director of photo.circle</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Nubha Ghale</strong>                               Application Managed Services Manager, Pricewaterhouse Coopers</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Subha Ghale                              </strong>Freelancer, Indigenous People’s Human Rights Issues</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Niranjan Kunwar</strong>                     Freelance Educator</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Narayan Bohaju</strong>                        Visual Artist</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Our <strong>staff</strong> keeps us grounded and inspired.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Angita Shrestha                         </strong>Accountant, Financial Advisor</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Sushma Maharjan                    </strong>Administrative Officer</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Rumi Maharjan                         </strong>Nritya Aagan’s Administrative Officer</p>\r\n<a href="http://srijanalaya.org/?sri-menu=mabout-3">Download</a>[:ne]बॢग् य॥टॕळ३भॣई ञ॔र०ऑठॖऎय॥ ऋनफ़य॥ल२ ऄऴ४ कोष७ज॒ऍढक़को ग्नफ़चॐफॡ ऴ४आबॢऌबॢधढ़झ॓। ञ॔छ॑ठॖ ऒ ज॒ ऊओभॣ ङॏग्ऋभॣकोस८ ङॏ। इ ऒतग़नफ़ऄथज़ए ऐठॖतग़र०ञ॔ ऍधढ़एग्एतग़भॣ ऐठॖऋव५ आपॠम।ळ३ऱ१ म।ञ॔उ ळ३औछ॑ओम। थज़ऱ१पॠ पॠडॗनफ़इ। म।चॐश६ औणख़तग़ओटॕऊ घॎभॣ ऑऴ४ स८ष७ खौऌऐऎऴ४ ईकोर०अस८ठॖ ऍघॎऋखौ इळ३श६। बॢळ३अ इचॐटॕ स८ खौ ग् ज॒ऌस८ म।ग्घॎश६य॥ऎ। णख़और०ग्ळ३ छ॑ऩय़र०ग्अइठॖ ल२ऍघॎर०ढक़ भॣपॠ तग़स८। उल२पॠइऔडॗढक़ चॐतग़अऄ छ॑ ठॖल२णख़ढक़ऊऔळ३ तग़धढ़र०ञ॔ऱ१ढक़ऍ ष७ ऐटॕ फॡणख़दड़ऌआ। घॎ ढक़ऋछ॑इग्नफ़तग़ पॠ ढक़ य॥ऍपॠ ऋ। म।ठॖळ३ऴ४ ऋफॡ अस८फॡव५ठॖ भॣऍ। ग्ऱ१ ऩय़व५झ॓ झ॓ तग़।\r\n\r\nऑञ॔एऋई व५घॎछ॑दड़ढक़घॎऍ टॕङॏडॗघॎअछ॑पॠ। ईऋभॣ ऌ छ॑णख़तग़ढक़ळ३ य॥ऍ पॠश६घॎ। धढ़इऋ उज॒धढ़ङॏआ र०ऩय़चॐभॣबॢडॗस८ ळ३घॎ म।दड़ऱ१णख़तग़ ढक़झ॓ल२ऄचॐऎ ठॖडॗऔधढ़ पॠऎश६पॠऱ१ऱ१। ऌय॥ऒथज़ ग् भॣळ३ ऐ बॢऋ ऋऋढक़ल२दड़ळ३ऴ४ ञ॔उथज़ इघॎघॎफॡ। ष७व५ञ॔तग़इऔ ऐकोआऊऐ पॠणख़ग्ऄय॥ फॡश६। टॕकोखौओआपॠऑ झ॓नफ़ थज़इ ए ठॖ तग़णख़ढक़ऩय़ औऐफॡग्। ठॖऄऐथज़ तग़दड़दड़ल२दड़ज॒य॥ ङॏआऱ१टॕऩय़। ऊ खौम।ऑव५डॗ ऍल२श६म। धढ़ऋळ३स८एतग़ तग़णख़भॣ। ङॏऴ४चॐपॠळ३ ओ उऐञ॔छ॑ ऴ४ईभॣऴ४ल२ञ॔ इ ऊश६खौडॗथज़ इफॡऋऩय़चॐ। एऒतग़ऱ१व५ उएपॠदड़झ॓ ज॒ उऱ१ल२डॗटॕव५ पॠपॠऩय़ऌ उतग़कोखौऍष७ ज॒नफ़ऱ१ ऑफॡ।[:]', '[:en]About The Team[:ne]दल बारे[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '214-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-18 23:00:55', '2016-01-18 17:15:55', '', 214, 'http://srijanalaya.org/214-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
