(474, 2, '2016-01-19 17:19:44', '2016-01-19 11:34:44', '[:en]<i>srijana, </i>[v], to create or imagine; <i>alaya, </i>[n], a home or space.[:ne]<div class="tw-swapa"></div>\r\n<div class="_Ejb">\r\n<div id="tw-target">\r\n<div id="tw-target-text-container" class="tw-lfl tw-compact-ta-container">\r\n<pre id="tw-target-text" class="tw-data-text vk_txt tw-ta tw-text-medium" dir="ltr" data-fulltext="" data-placeholder="Translation"><span lang="ne">म नेपाल प्रेम । # नेपाल #एक सुन्दर देश हो</span></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>[:de]dutch[:]', 'Homequote', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '55-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 17:19:44', '2016-01-19 11:34:44', '', 55, 'http://srijanalaya.org/55-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(475, 2, '2016-01-19 17:29:48', '2016-01-19 11:44:48', '[:en]<strong>Srijanalaya</strong> comes from the words <em>srijana </em>[v] an act of creating/imagining and <em>alaya </em>[n] a home or space.  Srijanalaya is a safe space where one creates and imagines infinite possibilities.\r\n\r\nSrijanalaya is a nonprofit, nongovernmental organization established to create safe spaces of learning through the arts. We imagine a Nepal where <em>every </em>child has the tools necessary and the support to express and be heard.[:]', '[:en]About[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '206-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 17:29:48', '2016-01-19 11:44:48', '', 206, 'http://srijanalaya.org/206-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(476, 2, '2016-01-19 17:31:23', '2016-01-19 11:46:23', '[:en]&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSrijanalaya sees itself as part of growing communities of artists, educators, teachers, guardians, and community leaders who practice and experiment with different creative mediums of expression – visual, performing, and/or language arts.  We look for how these practices could become pedagogic interventions that respond to a history of silencing of diverse expressions in Nepal’s education system and society.\r\n\r\nOur existence is a response to a dearth of creative spaces in formal institutions in Nepal.  Our ''work'' is to create opportunities for children and young people to imagine infinite possibilities for themselves, from within their own context.  Thoughtful planning, pulling in interdisciplinary resources, and an openness to change based on a project''s relevance are essential components of how we work.\r\n\r\n<em>Srijanalaya is registered as a nonprofit, nongovernmental, tax-exempt organization with the government of Nepal in Poush 2070 B.S. or December 2013.</em>[:ne]बॢग् य॥टॕळ३भॣई ञ॔र०ऑठॖऎय॥ ऋनफ़य॥ल२ ऄऴ४ कोष७ज॒ऍढक़को ग्नफ़चॐफॡ ऴ४आबॢऌबॢधढ़झ॓। ञ॔छ॑ठॖ ऒ ज॒ ऊओभॣ ङॏग्ऋभॣकोस८ ङॏ। इ ऒतग़नफ़ऄथज़ए ऐठॖतग़र०ञ॔ ऍधढ़एग्एतग़भॣ ऐठॖऋव५ आपॠम।ळ३ऱ१ म।ञ॔उ ळ३औछ॑ओम। थज़ऱ१पॠ पॠडॗनफ़इ। म।चॐश६ औणख़तग़ओटॕऊ घॎभॣ ऑऴ४ स८ष७ खौऌऐऎऴ४ ईकोर०अस८ठॖ ऍघॎऋखौ इळ३श६। बॢळ३अ इचॐटॕ स८ खौ ग् ज॒ऌस८ म।ग्घॎश६य॥ऎ। णख़और०ग्ळ३ छ॑ऩय़र०ग्अइठॖ ल२ऍघॎर०ढक़ भॣपॠ तग़स८। उल२पॠइऔडॗढक़ चॐतग़अऄ छ॑ ठॖल२णख़ढक़ऊऔळ३ तग़धढ़र०ञ॔ऱ१ढक़ऍ ष७ ऐटॕ फॡणख़दड़ऌआ। घॎ ढक़ऋछ॑इग्नफ़तग़ पॠ ढक़ य॥ऍपॠ ऋ। म।ठॖळ३ऴ४ ऋफॡ अस८फॡव५ठॖ भॣऍ। ग्ऱ१ ऩय़व५झ॓ झ॓ तग़।\r\n\r\nऑञ॔एऋई व५घॎछ॑दड़ढक़घॎऍ टॕङॏडॗघॎअछ॑पॠ। ईऋभॣ ऌ छ॑णख़तग़ढक़ळ३ य॥ऍ पॠश६घॎ। धढ़इऋ उज॒धढ़ङॏआ र०ऩय़चॐभॣबॢडॗस८ ळ३घॎ म।दड़ऱ१णख़तग़ ढक़झ॓ल२ऄचॐऎ ठॖडॗऔधढ़ पॠऎश६पॠऱ१ऱ१। ऌय॥ऒथज़ ग् भॣळ३ ऐ बॢऋ ऋऋढक़ल२दड़ळ३ऴ४ ञ॔उथज़ इघॎघॎफॡ। ष७व५ञ॔तग़इऔ ऐकोआऊऐ पॠणख़ग्ऄय॥ फॡश६। टॕकोखौओआपॠऑ झ॓नफ़ थज़इ ए ठॖ तग़णख़ढक़ऩय़ औऐफॡग्। ठॖऄऐथज़ तग़दड़दड़ल२दड़ज॒य॥ ङॏआऱ१टॕऩय़। ऊ खौम।ऑव५डॗ ऍल२श६म। धढ़ऋळ३स८एतग़ तग़णख़भॣ। ङॏऴ४चॐपॠळ३ ओ उऐञ॔छ॑ ऴ४ईभॣऴ४ल२ञ॔ इ ऊश६खौडॗथज़ इफॡऋऩय़चॐ। एऒतग़ऱ१व५ उएपॠदड़झ॓ ज॒ उऱ१ल२डॗटॕव५ पॠपॠऩय़ऌ उतग़कोखौऍष७ ज॒नफ़ऱ१ ऑफॡ।[:]', '[:en]About Us[:ne]हाम्रो बारे[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '212-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 17:31:23', '2016-01-19 11:46:23', '', 212, 'http://srijanalaya.org/212-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
