(515, 2, '2016-01-20 16:16:58', '2016-01-20 10:31:58', '[:en]Srijanalaya is a nonprofit, nongovernmental organization established to create safe spaces of learning through the arts. We imagine a Nepal where <em>every </em>child has the tools necessary and the support to express and be heard.\r\n\r\n<strong>Srijanalaya</strong> comes from the words <em>srijana </em>[v] to create/imagine and <em>alaya </em>[n] a home or space.[:]', '[:en]About[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '206-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-20 16:16:58', '2016-01-20 10:31:58', '', 206, 'http://srijanalaya.org/206-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
